[[Hutapiri]] (concentration in English) zvinoreva huwandu hwechiri kutsvakwa mudutu rezvinhu zviri kutarirwa. Kana gold ichicherwa [[chitofu]] chinobuda kumugodhi chinkwanisa kunge chine [[hutapiri]] hunoita 2 gram/tonne. Panozosvika kunatswa kuReserve Bank chidhinha che gold chinenge chava nehutapiri hunoita 99% zvichikwira.

[[Mutape]] zvinoreva izvo zvinobatwa zvinenge zvawedzerwa hutapiri nemitowo inopatsanura [[mambara]] kubva ku[[chitofu]]. Hutapiri hwemuchenga une mari hunenge hwawanda mumutape.
